VALUES ('589569eb-4ddc-4ba2-8c17-a8d9d46d699f', 'In triangle $ABC$ shown, $m\angle B = 60°$ and $m\angle A = 96°$. What is $m\angle C$?', '<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 280 200" aria-label="Triangle diagram">
